> Didn't implement StreamLoadAction?

Yes, brpc does not support continuous reception with http, ![refer to](https://github.com/apache/brpc/issues/1217). After discussing with @dataroaring, we decided to implement it in another way, and the implementation will be in another pr, so that @xiaojunjie is able to start https works smoothly.  
Currently, I am focusing on regression-test and will make it completed as soon as possible.

Hello, let me answer a few questions separately.
The first problem of not obtaining the variable value correctly is actually because the variable is not entered correctly. This is no problem. In the final analysis, it is caused by the third problem.
Ditto for the second question
Sorry for the third question, the document here is indeed missing BROKER_NAME, thanks for the correction, the format of BROKER_ADDR should be BROKER_NAME:BROLER_HOST:BROKER_PORT
